title: Strangelove's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Chinese, Indian, International, Italian, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. "Vegans, vegetarians and carnivores alike find a welcoming home here at Strangelove's."  Variety of vegan and vegetarian options, including vegan: sides, appetizers, sandwiches, salads, entries, and even a vegan desert.  The food encompasses a wide variety ethnicities as well as American food and has a great beer selection.
